data.description: Explore your ideal San Antonio home, conveniently located near the thriving community of  Brooks City Base. This property features recent upgrades, including energy-efficient solar panels, a new HVAC system, fresh interior paint, and a spacious shed in the backyard. With high ceilings, a wood-burning fireplace, a carport, and a separate living and dining area, you can embrace comfortable living within a thriving community. Your dream home is ready for you!
